title: Converse Rubber Tracks - Ealing
description:
www.converse-music.com

Converse Rubber Tracks is a professional recording studio that takes up residency in different boroughs throughout London, offering the city’s most exciting new talent free recording and mixing time.

Following on from the residency at Snap Studios in Haringey, the series is now making its way to the London Borough of Ealing. Applications to record in the borough's legendary Kore Studios in April are now open at www.converse.co.uk/rubber-tracks
